      <Text>Starting at 3rd level, when you cast mage hand, you can make the spectral hand invisible, and you can perform the following additional tasks with it:
â€¢ You can stow one object the hand is holding in a container worn or carried by another creature.
â€¢ You can retrieve an object in a container worn or carried by another creature.
