You can perform one of these tasks without being noticed by a creature if you succeed on a Dexterity (Sleight of Hand) check contested by the creatureâ€™s Wisdom (Perception) check. 
In addition, you can use the bonus action granted by your Cunning Action to control the hand.</Text>
